  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Trail Mix</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/32px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Trail Mix</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruit\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fruit\">Fruit</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">item</a> introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Reign of Giants\">Reign of Giants</a></i> DLC. It is cooked in a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> by combining 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Birchnut\" title=\"Birchnut\">Roasted Birchnut</a>, 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berries\" title=\"Berries\">Berry</a>, and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruit\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fruit\">Fruit</a>.\n</p><p>Trail Mix is one of the cheapest healing dishes that can be made, restoring more <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\">Health</a> than its components, making it a useful early game healing item.  However, it restores less total <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\">Hunger</a> than its individual ingredients.\n</p><p>Trail Mix is one of the better healing items for <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Beefalo\" title=\"Beefalo\">Beefalo</a>, for which it restores 120 health (due to their 4x food health multiplier). It can be made earlier in the game than <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragonpie\" title=\"Dragonpie\">Dragonpie</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Birchnut\" title=\"Roasted Birchnut\"><img alt=\"Roasted Birchnut.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roasted_Birchnut.png?9d5e98\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berries\" title=\"Berries\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\"><img alt=\"Fruits Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fruits_Crock_Pot.png?8542cd\" width=\"375\" height=\"108\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meats_Crock_Pot.png?bb1767\" width=\"580\" height=\"108\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Vegetables Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Vegetables_Crock_Pot.png?fc26f1\" width=\"466\" height=\"130\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\"><img alt=\"Eggs Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Eggs_Crock_Pot.png?afac2d\" width=\"175\" height=\"82\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy_product\" title=\"Dairy product\"><img alt=\"Dairy product.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dairy_product.png?dcc466\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Birchnut\" title=\"Roasted Birchnut\"><img alt=\"Roasted Birchnut.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roasted_Birchnut.png?9d5e98\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\"><img alt=\"Fruit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fruit.png?853057\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Trail_Mix\" title=\"Trail Mix\"><img alt=\"Trail Mix.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Trail_Mix.png?a1c101\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Birchnut\" title=\"Roasted Birchnut\"><img alt=\"Roasted Birchnut.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roasted_Birchnut.png?9d5e98\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berries\" title=\"Berries\"><img alt=\"Berries.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berries.png?629a2e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Trail_Mix\" title=\"Trail Mix\"><img alt=\"Trail Mix.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Trail_Mix.png?a1c101\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Birchnut\" title=\"Roasted Birchnut\"><img alt=\"Roasted Birchnut.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roasted_Birchnut.png?9d5e98\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pomegranates\" title=\"Pomegranates\"><img alt=\"Pomegranates.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pomegranates.png?f50549\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Trail_Mix\" title=\"Trail Mix\"><img alt=\"Trail Mix.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Trail_Mix.png?a1c101\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Birchnut\" title=\"Roasted Birchnut\"><img alt=\"Roasted Birchnut.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roasted_Birchnut.png?9d5e98\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Trail_Mix\" title=\"Trail Mix\"><img alt=\"Trail Mix.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Trail_Mix.png?a1c101\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Birchnut\" title=\"Roasted Birchnut\"><img alt=\"Roasted Birchnut.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roasted_Birchnut.png?9d5e98\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Trail_Mix\" title=\"Trail Mix\"><img alt=\"Trail Mix.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Trail_Mix.png?a1c101\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Trail_Mix\" title=\"Trail Mix\"><img alt=\"Trail Mix.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Trail_Mix.png?a1c101\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Icon\" title=\"Pig Icon\"><img alt=\"Pig Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Pig_Icon.png/42px-Pig_Icon.png?2561d3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Manure\" title=\"Manure\"><img alt=\"Manure.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Manure.png?f3cf48\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Trail_Mix_128x128.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\"><img alt=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Trail_Mix_128x128.png/120px-Trail_Mix_128x128.png?5237ea\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Trail_Mix#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Trail_Mix#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
