  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Exclusivity|Reign of Giants|Don't Starve Together}}\n__NOTOC__\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = Trail Mix.png\n|image = Trail Mix Dropped.png\n|stack = 40\n|spawnCode = \"trailmix\"\n|hpRestored = 30\n|hungerRestored = 12.5\n|sanityRestored = 5\n|cooktime = 10 sec\n|priority = 10\n|spoil = 15 Days\n|canBeBurned=1\n|foodType = [[Veggie]] [[File:Veggie.png|32px|link=Veggie]]\n|foodRecipe ={{Pic|32px|Roasted Birchnut}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Berry}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Fruit}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x1\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = A healthy, natural snack.\n|willow = Crunch crunch crunch.\n|wolfgang = Berries and nuts, berries and nuts!\n|wendy = A handful of sustenance.\n|wx78 = HIGHLY NUTRITIONAL\n|wickerbottom = Mmmm, natural!\n|woodie = The perfect snack for a day of chopping.\n|maxwell = Nuts and berries. No bolts.\n|wagstaff = Fascinating. A translucent bag just spontaneously materialized!\n|wigfrid = Meat öf a nut is nöt true meat.\n|webber = Crunchy and healthy.\n|walani = Protein!\n|warly = Energy food!\n|woodlegs = I prefer sea snacks.\n|wilba = 'TIS MIX OF FOODS\n|wormwood = Belly stuff for belly\n|wheeler = Ready for a hike.\n|winona = All the energy you need for a long day at work.\n|wortox = Looks chewy. I hate chewing.\n|wurt = Crunch, crunch, crunch!\n|walter = The snack of choice for all intrepid explorers!\n|wanda = I prefer the version that has little bits of candy in it...\n|choose = walter\n}}\n'''Trail Mix''' is a [[Fruit]] [[Food]] [[item]] introduced in the ''[[Reign of Giants]]'' DLC. It is cooked in a [[Crock Pot]] by combining 1 [[Birchnut|Roasted Birchnut]], 1 [[Berries|Berry]], and 1 [[Fruit]].\n\nTrail Mix is one of the cheapest healing dishes that can be made, restoring more [[Health]] than its components, making it a useful early game healing item.  However, it restores less total [[Hunger]] than its individual ingredients.\n\nTrail Mix is one of the better healing items for [[Beefalo]], for which it restores 120 health (due to their 4x food health multiplier). It can be made earlier in the game than [[Dragonpie]].\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires: [[File:Roasted Birchnut.png|link=Roasted Birchnut]]\n* Requires: [[File:Berry.png|link=Berries]]\n* Requires: [[File:Fruits Crock Pot.png|link=Fruit]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Meats Crock Pot.png|link=Meats]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Vegetables Crock Pot.png|link=Vegetables]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Eggs Crock Pot.png|link=Eggs]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Dairy product.png|link=Dairy product]]\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Roasted Birchnut\n|item2 = Berry\n|item3 = Fruit\n|item4 = Filler\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Trail Mix\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Roasted Birchnut\n|item2 = Berries\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Trail Mix\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Roasted Birchnut\n|item2 = Berry\n|item3 = Pomegranates\n|item4 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Trail Mix\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Roasted Birchnut\n|item2 = Berry\n|count2 = 3\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Trail Mix\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Roasted Birchnut \n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Berry\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Trail Mix\n}}\n\n== {{pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item = Trail Mix\n|tool = Pig Icon\n|result = Manure\n}}\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nTrail Mix 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\n</gallery>\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n[[fr:Mélange montagnard]]\n[[Category:Items]]\n[[Category:Food]]\n[[Category:Healing]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]"
